# panik :question:
paniks all the time when something goes wrong

![panik](https://i.imgur.com/BjKTE8m.jpeg)

# instal
`pipinstal panik`
if the abov dont work
`pip install .`
if the abov dont work
`pip install panik`

# execut
`import panik`
